| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4991 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8bfdf409-5f4a-5748-b978-7a987c7d9401"
